{"tid":2459290,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"犯法要負責｜警員涉以虛假資料騙貸款 獲准保釋惟須先交出旅遊證件包括BNO","createTime":"2021-03-24T05:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T07:16:57.000Z","uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"88864f3f2e10b7715a2c307283e298c9d801b50b","tid":2459290,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:32:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210324/N2B3T6ZIE5BFZOBCUHN5Y25NPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210324%2FN2B3T6ZIE5BFZOBCUHN5Y25NPQ%2F&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2H4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=3cab7d46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210324%2FN2B3T6ZIE5BFZOBCUHN5Y25NPQ%2F&h=d5697aaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210324/N2B3T6ZIE5BFZOBCUHN5Y25NPQ/</a>"},{"pid":"de61a4feb085938ba6357f0c71c2ef2dd2f452a5","tid":2459290,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:33:32.000Z","msg":"現役警員涉嫌於5年內三度向俗稱「遮仔會」的警察儲蓄互助社提交虛假資料，藉此騙取約12.5萬元貸款。東九龍重案組探員上月拘捕該名涉案警員，控以三項欺詐罪。案件今天於觀塘裁判法院提堂，辯方申請暫緩答辯及保釋候訊。主任裁判官錢禮下令將被告還柙，直至他交出所有旅遊證件，包括BNO。被告警員隨即被庭警帶進犯人欄步入羈留室。<br />\n<br />\n身材高大健碩的被告黃新阩（39歲），又名黃茂享，控罪書未有如常列出被告職業。據悉被告已遭停職。控罪書指被告於2013年、2015年及2017年三度向警察儲蓄互助社提交虛假資料，藉此騙取一筆約12.5萬元貸款。<br />\n<br />\n辯方庭上申請暫緩答辯，要求案件押後至5月18日，其間等候被告聘請私人律師代表出庭應訊。控方不反對申請，惟要求增加不得離港及交出旅遊證件、包括BNO等多項保釋條件。裁判官批准被告以500元保釋外出，惟需等候他交出所有旅遊證件始能獲釋，其間須還柙看管。"},{"pid":"6ce7613dc86c807784a0b7a1184317a308d1f90f","tid":2459290,"uid":159582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:38:19.000Z","msg":"又承認返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5090d65e2000c5509734ee2c2af52e8bd3cca175","tid":2459290,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:40:56.000Z","msg":"呃得十二萬 之前ot錢都唔止啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afb1f1940478db7c5edfb11cbf8bc3c4faab945","tid":2459290,"uid":60145,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:41:57.000Z","msg":"全球不包括香港<br />\n旅遊証件包括BNO"},{"pid":"bed9fb32a7fca2cb5b68dff16305d89cd25519d8","tid":2459290,"uid":71393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:42:45.000Z","msg":"呃12萬只要500元保釋金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483a38e39e3e3067fb804df7c84e70a54ef8eb31","tid":2459290,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:47:24.000Z","msg":"欺騙黨中央同國家以及人民感情，判處死刑!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f25b0af32924c1647a3eb596857103a7fd05743","tid":2459290,"uid":59037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T06:43:22.000Z","msg":"做狗拎BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdcbbbb4d61f79db998939a45a8bfb580a078af","tid":2459290,"uid":363581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T06:44:06.000Z","msg":"condom仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12baeb1ff136576c7f883307560504cf25a26597","tid":2459290,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XeADPyK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXeADPyK.gif&h=675635f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3362cb2c698063b8faeb4b9e5ed7a999b638cb7b","tid":2459290,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T07:16:57.000Z","msg":"分開講就得架啦？<br />\n咁bno 當係咩呀？"}]}